  "notes": "Fourth floor of the Olivine Lighthouse. Has two trainers: Sailor Kent (2x Krabby with move sets, hints about Cianwood Pharmacy) and Lass Connie (Marill Lv21, came to bring Jasmine back to the Gym). Sailor Kent's after-battle dialogue is an explicit pointer directing the player to Cianwood for the SecretPotion. The floor is heavily connected to both 3F below and 5F above with 10 warp events total across multiple staircase routes. No items on this floor. Lass Connie is positioned near the north, Sailor Kent near the south-center."
